<p><b>Jonathan Paul Ive</b>, <a href="/wiki/Order_of_the_British_Empire" title="Order of the British Empire">CBE</a> (born February, 1967) is a <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">British</a> designer and the <a href="/wiki/Senior_Vice_President" title="Senior Vice President" class="mw-redirect">Senior Vice President</a> of <a href="/wiki/Industrial_Design" title="Industrial Design" class="mw-redirect">Industrial Design</a> at <a href="/wiki/Apple_Inc" title="Apple Inc" class="mw-redirect">Apple Inc</a>. He is internationally renowned as the principal designer of the <a href="/wiki/IMac" title="IMac">iMac</a>, aluminum and titanium <a href="/wiki/PowerBook_G4" title="PowerBook G4">PowerBook G4</a>, <a href="/wiki/MacBook" title="MacBook">MacBook</a>, <a href="/wiki/MacBook_Pro#Unibody_MacBook_Pro" title="MacBook Pro">unibody MacBook Pro</a>, <a href="/wiki/IPod" title="IPod">iPod</a> and <a href="/wiki/IPhone" title="IPhone">iPhone</a>.</p>
